2072.subject: ASAP
2072.descrlong: Provides supplemental support for WRT 95 Writing Workshop course. Students work in small groups with a tutor from the Academic Skills Achievement Program (ASAP) and focus on reading strategies and study skills. Groups meet one hour per week. Credit/no credit only.
